description:
Leading to War is a website / film that chronicles the US Government&amp;#039;s use of deception and misinformation that led to the 2003 invasion of Iraq, which has resulted in, as of September 2007, more than 1,000,000 dead Iraqis*. That number of casualties is most unfortunate. Please watch this film and see for yourself what transpired. Hindsight is 20/20 but we should be able to take from the film that the media and the government are never to be completely trusted, especially when it comes to legitimizing the use of military force.

